/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both Elon Musk and J.K. Rowling have been named in a cyberbullying lawsuit filed by Imane Khelif following the abuse she received throughout the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.487549690757938e-15, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 328, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif competed at the Tokyo Olympics three years ago to zero furore, but her participation in Paris caused a stir due to her failing an unspecified gender eligibility test administered by the International Boxing Association (IBA) at the women's world championships in 2023.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999376311755, \"rank\": 6.236883498724925e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9586255029302584e-19, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9996374109139993, \"rank\": 0.0003615548515472189, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) disputed the test and questioned its legitimacy and ruled her eligible to compete in Paris.Khelif's participation led to a gender row erupting at the Olympics and she faced heavy abuse online.The Algerian, who went on to win Olympic gold in the women's 66kg category, has now filed a cyberbullying lawsuit to the Paris public prosecutor's office.Khelif's lawyer, Nabil Boudi, told Variety that both Musk and Rowling were named in the lawsuit after comments they both made on social media.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9992503425212355, \"rank\": 0.0004961366918650532, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999376311755, \"rank\": 6.236883498724925e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/